8a01			; 
8a01			; Multiply 8-bit value with a 16-bit value (right rotating) 
8a01			; In: Multiply A with DE 
8a01			;      Put lowest value in A for most efficient calculation 
8a01			; Out: HL = result 
8a01			; 
8a01			Mult12R: 
8a01 21 00 00		    ld hl,0 
8a04			Mult12R_Loop: 
8a04 cb 3f		    srl a 
8a06 30 01		    jr nc,Mult12R_NoAdd 
8a08 19			    add hl,de 
8a09			Mult12R_NoAdd: 
8a09 cb 23		    sla e 
8a0b cb 12		    rl d 
8a0d b7			    or a 
8a0e c2 04 8a		    jp nz,Mult12R_Loop 
8a11 c9			    ret 
