9b71			; 
9b71			; 
9b71			; define linked list: 
9b71			; 
9b71			; 1. compiled byte op code 
9b71			; 2. len of text word 
9b71			; 3. text word 
9b71			; 4. ptr to next dictionary word 
9b71			; 5. asm, calls etc for the word 
9b71			; 
9b71			;  if 1 == 0 then last word in dict  
9b71			;   
9b71			; set the start of dictionary scanning to be in ram and the last word point to the system dict 
